# DD-2: Rollback Readiness
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Every production release

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Rollback Plan: Predefined procedure to revert deployments safely.

ENFORCE: A tested rollback plan must exist and be reviewed before every release.
PROHIBIT: Deploying without a rollback plan; ad-hoc rollbacks without approval.
ON VIOLATION: Halt deployment → escalate to DevOps Lead.
